on.=20
The Supreme Court last week heard oral arguments in a case that could be a w=
atershed for the U.S. power industry and decide whether FERC has the right t=
o drive competition on state transmission networks.=20
In a classic battle of state versus federal jurisdictional turf, Enron wants=
